<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBd9_00085" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBd9_00085_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><sampling type="start" />根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おまえがしんでからは商売にも出ないで、念仏ばかり申しています。</sentence>
<sentence>どうぞ怒って下さるな。</sentence>
<sentence>俺はあとから早くいきたい。</sentence>
<sentence>どうぞ<ruby rubyText="はん">半</ruby><ruby rubyText="ざ">座</ruby>を分けて待っておいで。</sentence>
<sentence>半座がなければ芋の葉でもかまわないから。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏…」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">といっていると、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">兄</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「オイ、静かにしろ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">しっかりマッチをおっことすな」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「でえじょうぶだ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">兄</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「火をつけたか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「<ruby rubyText="ごう">豪</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぎ">気</ruby>にみえるな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">兄</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「静かにしろ…やい、そりゃどうだ…見えたか…お気がつかれたか…やい…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　これを見ると、根次兵衛は一生懸命に、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏お<ruby rubyText="きん">金</ruby>やお金や、浮かんで下さいまし…南無阿弥陀仏南無阿弥陀仏」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　屋根にいる両人はこれを聞きましてきりきりとかの火の玉をあげまして<ruby rubyText="うち">自宅</ruby>へ帰ってまいりました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">兄</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うまくいったなあ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「えー、浮かんで下さいましとは、たしかに魂と思っているにちげえねえ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">寸法通り明日の朝まいります」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<sentence type="quasi">と別れてその晩はふせり、朝になりますと熊公は、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お早うございます、根次兵衛さん」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「これは熊さんでございますか、どうぞこちらへ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">この間はまたとむらいの節はいろいろお手伝い下さいましてありがとう存じます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「どういたしまして。</sentence>
<sentence>なんしろどうもとんだことでございます。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">さぞお力落としで日に増しおさびしゅうございましょう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ありがとうございます」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「だけれども、そうしてしじゅう仏壇へ向いてお念仏を申したら、<ruby rubyText="おかみ">細君</ruby>さんがさぞ浮かばれることでございましょう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「へえ、あれは浮かばれませんでございますよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「どういうわけで」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「四十九日は<ruby rubyText="や">屋</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="むね">棟</ruby>に魂がいますと申します。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">その魂がゆうべ出ましたよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「しめた」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんでございます」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なに、こちらのことで…とんだことで大変なことでございます…へえ…女てえもんは気の小せえもんで、つまらないという心が出るから大変でげす…へえ、どうも世の中にいくらもあるんで、金や着物に気が残って寺へ納めてしまえば出っこねえ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「へえなるほど。</sentence>
<sentence>これは金や着物に気が残っています。</sentence>
<sentence>そうでございますか、いいことをうかがいます。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">早速納めましょう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「いや、わっちが納めてあげましょう」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「それでは恐れいります」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「なによろしゅうございます。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">風呂敷を持って来たからこのうちへお入れなさい」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「風呂敷を」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ちと困った。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">なんでございます、ちょいと買い物があって」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「へえ、なんでございます」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「焼き芋を二十五銭買おうと思って」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「さようでございますか…じゃ、なにぶん願います。</sentence>
<sentence>熊さん、この<ruby rubyText="たん">簞</ruby><ruby rubyText="す">笥</ruby>でも何でもみんなあれのものでございます。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">この簞笥を見るにつけても思いの<ruby rubyText="たね">種</ruby>でございます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">熊</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そうでございます。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">お気の毒でございます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">根</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あれがお屋敷からさが<sampling type="end" />ってまいりました時塗った簞笥でございましたが、これはおかしいからあたりめえなのをと申して、小伝馬町の角の小川で買いました。</sentence>
<sentence>十五円五十銭、人力車代が十二銭五厘で買ってまいりました。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">これをみるにつけても涙の種でございます」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
